Ganesha Sthuthi

42:29.929 --> 42:31.959
Who knows all the Ganesha Sthuthi to be sung?

42:32.969 --> 42:34.909
Or you know Atharva Sheersh?

42:53.879 --> 42:55.899
Because Ganesha is the One, you see,

42:55.899 --> 42:57.879
who is sitting on Mooladhara,

42:57.879 --> 43:01.919
and it is He who is the One who puts you onto the left side.

43:01.919 --> 43:03.919
He throws you all the time.

43:04.909 --> 43:08.959
And it is Mahavira who tries to save you and to correct you.

43:09.959 --> 43:12.909
So there are two forces working.

